Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.41,0:00:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hook a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why that getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a Fish and Water
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like fishing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna land a whopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's biting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilch. Today was the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He already said he caught nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr, I need food, food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come, Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't feel like eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you dislike the taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was back when Takami \Nhad been chosen as the family heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd begun to spend \Na lot more time apart from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd been talking less.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,While I didn't feel like I was lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it was as if Takami had suddenly gone far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One such day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I withstood it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win again today, Takami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that guy again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona Ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage check!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I beat Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He and Takami were always together... \Nat least, that was my initial impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Takami had never shown a face like that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Young miss, your teacher is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Young miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For a time, Bro didn't visit at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because Takami had grown busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I spent my days just going \Nbetween home and school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd realized that was \Nthe sort of family we were,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and thought that I myself needed \Nto become a person suitable for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the deck my brother had stopped using...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that those days \Nwould never again return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my reunion with Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, I found out he'd come to trim the tree \Nin the garden, at my brother's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Takami left a short while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we had a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be counting on you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like calling out to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what would we even talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't like he knew me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let this chance slip away, \Nwe may never meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were my thoughts as I got out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the amusement park \NI'd often visited when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After having not seen it in so long, \NI was surprised at how rundown it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,People?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cardfighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner: Danji Momoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Aren't you... Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what, hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!\NMy bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I reacted by running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't even thanked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, fretting over his sunglasses, \NI went and got a new pair for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But, when and how would I give them to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't be sure if he'd even accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"What am I doing?" I wondered to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here! Come out a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I broke your hair ornament!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this will do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You got one for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures that I'd get the style wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I also felt bad about breaking your sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This calls for an exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a busy time of year right now, \Nalways warming up then cooling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You play Vanguard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so?! \NYou're welcome any time you want a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't cardfight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never had one? \NThen how would you know you can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sure chilly once the sun goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind against my cheeks felt refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our team is Blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Black...out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody! This is Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my friend. Tell her hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you again, Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Great to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to change my mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:10:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're witnessing the birth of a new Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He burst out singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you do for a birth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's her birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What else would I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to them, \NI felt like I had been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,First period today features \Na special lesson on traffic safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Lesson: Traffic Safety\NFirst period today features \Na special lesson on traffic safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A police officer is here to speak to you all,\NSpecial Lesson: Traffic Safety
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so please listen closely.\NSpecial Lesson: Traffic Safety
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so please listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Tomari Seto, from the Traffic Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you there! If you would sit down, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to avoid traffic accidents, you need:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,safety confirmation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and hazard anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You look both ways before crossing the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is safety confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And for hazard anticipation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you think about how a car or pedestrian \Ncould suddenly come around a blind corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering possible incidents in advance \Nallows you to deal with them promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hazard anticipation," huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are times when \Noverthinking is what leads to danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Specifically, when it involves the guy you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Ms. Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do if he comes around that corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he see me looking weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How's my hair? My makeup? Is my face puffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And while you're doing that:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ka-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize he's all you can think about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this feeling? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The brakes! Just! Won't! Work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Screech!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Seto, could I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! We were just starting to have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Class, treat the rest of \Nfirst period as study hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?!\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wasn't it helpful?\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I went out of my way \Nto give you a special lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Special lesson?! For what purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you wish to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you've been all gloomy, Meg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a place for you \Nto forget your cares and have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you've been hanging around \Nwith that sour look and acting gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Yu-yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakusa, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to attend her special lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's not something \Nfor me to learn from you, Tomari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand a thing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww! Zakusa, Meg's being mean to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll console you, if it helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, is that a promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I make tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya, you guys arguing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, would you shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, the rule is for disputes \Nto be settled by cardfights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me, Little Miss Gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm not gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi and Tomari are having a Cardfight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's your favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first fight in ages! I'm getting chills!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll handle commentary in my place, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, Megumi and Tomari's cardfight begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't personally seen these two \Nbattle before, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what sort of fight \Nis about to unfold before us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Kyanite Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Its skill activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I add Galaxy Control Prison, \NGalactolus to my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and then put it into the Order Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna show you how an adult fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,An "adult," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who's an adult on the outside, \Nbut a child inside, is the nastiest of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, even after becoming \Nan adult, they're still a child--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, who's this about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You really need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi calls unit after unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another intense assault from her today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fighting like you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With the plays you always use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, it's so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you! Nothing's gonna change!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when you won't take \Nyour big sister's advice, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for a spanking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Risatt Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Its skill activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I imprison one of my opponent's cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tomari's Police Prison Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Locking an opponent's card in prison \Nmakes it unavailable to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With Agra Luge's skill, I imprison Agleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With Chevalstud's skill, I imprison Dooger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's arresting the units on the board, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless Megumi pays the cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,she won't be able to release \Nher imprisoned units!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to your cold jail cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it to your liking, young miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As always, you fight dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an adult fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you not misrepresent \Nan old lady's pigheadedness as "adult"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Beg pardon? I couldn't quite hear you, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you losing your hearing, granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ka-clang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you afraid of drawing \Nthe wrath of a police officer, Meg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?! I'm gonna kick your butt, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand to hear any more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody please take over the commentary for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Magnolia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, release Dooger to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi pays the cost to free her friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for being locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks to me that you're bound up \Nby something else, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been hesitant and gloomy for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got you so unhappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you unhappy about the kid who's barely joined \Nand yet steadily gaining in importance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or about the man who won't look your way, \Nno matter how much time passes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or about yourself, \Nfor being troubled by such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd best confess to everything, lovelorn maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Seraph Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Further, I call two Agra Luge \Nand a Kyanite Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Its skill activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disciplining this girl \Nwho can't be honest with herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm at it, I'll also teach you \Nhow to behave toward your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything besides her Vanguard \Nhas been put into prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Seraph Snow attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The more units I have imprisoned, \Nthe stronger my deck gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seraph Snow's powered-up ability \Ngives it a triple drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Double critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A double?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she has two critical triggers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari is one attractive woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because \NI'm always on my best behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Megumi hasn't drawn \Neven one trigger, and has 5 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,With one card in hand, \Nand her Vanguard all alone on the board,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's light on the red-- \Ner, right on the ledge! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as you said, Tomari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't honest with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, finally?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However... you had me all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,None of those were the reason why!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona Ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You had it all along?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you often say, \N"Trouble can be opportunity"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Counterblast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, return to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Paying the cost, she releases \Ncard after card from prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tactic only made possible \Nby taking all those attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My prison...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...has...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of everything, \Nby Persona Riding on Magnolia,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,all her units in the back row \Ngain the ability to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, it's a surging wave \Nof six attacks in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna struggle like an adult to the very end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't those two arguing just a moment ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's like nothing's been resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship born from \Na serious exchange of blows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But--\NNow that's manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji, did you pay the electric bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji didn't pay the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get on!\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my treat today!\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No telling my butler, okay?\NWonder Hill: Land of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No telling my butler, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tomari.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can manage this much, even on my salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad I met all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachiban Ramen\NMeg...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if you eat at this hour, \Nyou'll need to diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine! I'm still young!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wound up stuffing myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you're fretting about or wanting to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you still get hungry, and morning still comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi! Tomari!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro?! And everyone else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Warming of water hails the coming of spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A year does pass quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'd planned to catch \Na great big fish to celebrate, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Today will be my treat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat as much as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomari, let's have another bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you can still eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have heart-warming karamen noodles. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.83,0:23:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And hang on, pay the electric bill first, Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.20,0:23:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu, hurry up and join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.41,0:25:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.80,0:25:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.87,0:26:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's feeding time, all you card-loving \Nand card-possessed spirits out there!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.34,0:26:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm introducing my card, \NAurora Battle Princess, Seraph Snow!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.45,0:26:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With one Counterblast, Seraph Snow can send \Ntwo opposing units directly to a cold jail cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.16,0:26:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to pop 'em in the slammer! 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.12,0:26:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, if you have at least three cards \Nin custody, it gets an extra drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.85,0:26:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent! Fantastic! Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.52,0:26:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.28,0:26:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.29,0:26:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Overnight Statue 
